rve people's emotions and change your approach depending on them.<br></li><li><strong>Widened perspective</strong>: Inspect selected areas through panoramic view.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571090/extras/08dcf29ed2c87a29715729a56804d58e.avif?t=1721047447\" width=618 height=94 /></span><br>3 cases set in the present 21st Century!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Investigation</strong>: Study the surrounding and characters then write it down in your journal.<br></li><li><strong>Inventory</strong>: Collect evidence and show them to suspects for view their reactions.<br></li><li><strong>Maps</strong>: Several different location to choose to visit.<br></li><li><strong>Interrogate</strong>: Battle of wits, argument and prove who is behind the crimes.</li></ul>",
